			<span>设计</span>
		</a>
		<h1 class="title">现在，最酷的事是到木工坊里做一把自己的椅子</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王雯婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-09 08:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
		<img src="/system/articles/longshows/12868/medium/12868.jpg?1439177897" alt="" />
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="12868" data-title="《现在，最酷的事是到木工坊里做一把自己的椅子》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/12868/medium/12868.jpg?1438656670" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/12868.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
